caption.title: Phylogeny tree of DENV-2 serotype constructed using BEAST v2.5.1 using Gamma+I+T93 substitution model against Dengue genotyping database.
caption.p: All the sequences in the tree are labelled as; accession no._country year of isolation genotype. Tree is labelled with posterior probability at node. Highlighted area in the tree is being zoomed out at right side of figure where sequences from Nepal are shown. Detail tree with all of the sequences used for genotyping is shown in S2 Fig.
